        public SddcUserConfiguration.Builder setRouteAggregationEnabled(java.lang.Boolean routeAggregationEnabled)
        Flag to indicate if route aggregation is supported on a provider environment. Upstream consumers like HCX, WCP uses this attribute to find out if route aggregation APIs can be used on a provider environment. This property may be present in responses from the server, but if it is present in a request to server it will be ignored.
